It compiles fine without the code in NPCoption2, but if I add the code in there it doesn't work. Heres my code:
[code] case 362: p.viewings = 1; p.shopid = 2; p.frames.showInterface(p, 278); p.frames.setItems(p, 278, 89, 94, p.shop2, p.shop2n); p.frames.setString(p, "Starter's Shop", 278, 88); break; [/code]
I have added shops on other servers, each working fine. But on this server, there was no shops so I decided to try to add one.
Someone help?
